data.description: Introducing an unique upcoming opportunity in Indian Palms Country Club! This 3-bedroom, 3-bath gem comes with a detached casita, offering versatile living spaces for your unique needs. Investors do you have two opportunities for income with this property. Homeowners live in one unit and rent out the home or vice versa. Whatever your needs are this home has it all!Home features newer carpeting, LED lighting that illuminates every corner, and freshly painted walls adorned with the sophisticated Greek Villa Sherwin Williams paint. The heart of this home boasts beautiful cabinetry with gen electric appliances, refrigerator is brand new ensuring both style and functionality.With a 2-car garage and an additional golf cart garage, convenience meets elegance. Spanning 1,943 sq ft, this residence offers breathtaking views of the lake and green belt, creating a serene and picturesque backdrop for your everyday living.This short term rental approved home is walking distance to the iconic Polo grounds, home to Coachella Fest  & Stagecoach. Immerse yourself in the vibrant energy of these iconic events.An outstanding feature of this property is its assumable VA loan on approved credit providing a rare opportunity for a seamless transition. Don't miss the chance to make this dream home yours - where style, comfort, and the allure of Indian Palms Country Club living come together.
